02:37.335 --> 02:39.565
I had a fabulous time, Wesley.

02:40.205 --> 02:44.005
Why don't you come in?
Don't be silly, they won't be up for hours.

02:46.712 --> 02:48.441
Night, Sister Mary Margaret.

02:50.615 --> 02:53.345
Daddy, have you lost weight?

02:53.518 --> 02:54.951
Hilary.

02:56.021 --> 02:58.683
