than fancy clothes and big houses.

17:21.886 --> 17:23.353
What have you been smoking?

17:26.790 --> 17:29.521
Y o, Uncle Phil,
how you going to play a nephew?

17:30.194 --> 17:31.786
On his behind, Will.

17:34.265 --> 17:37.325
