for some milk and cookies.

17:37.702 --> 17:40.330
That honey was old enough
to be your mother.

17:42.139 --> 17:44.630
Word up, and she was divorced, too.

17:47.044 --> 17:48.807
Parents just don't understand.

17:51.382 --> 17:54.044
Hey, big guy,
got time to read me a bedtime story?

17:54.118 --> 17:58.487
Sure, Carlton, what's it going to be?
<i>Cat /n The Hat</i> or <i>Curious George?</i>

17:58.556 --> 18:02.515
No, <i>The Wa// Street Journa/,</i>
the part where AMC goes belly up.

18:04.795 --> 18:06.729
Are you sure we're all related?

18:08.699 --> 18:11.668
Mom, Dad, I've been thinking it over...

18:11.869 --> 18:14.736
and I've decided what I want to be
when I grow up.

18:14.805 --> 18:15.965
What, tall?

18:19.477 --> 18:23.072
- That's nice, honey, what?
- President of the United States.

18:23.414 --> 18:25.644
Well, that would make me
very proud, Carlton.

18:25.716 --> 18:28.947
Imagine, my son,
the country's first black president.

18:29.887 --> 18:31.081
I'm black?

18:44.268 --> 18:45.462
Hello?

18:47.138 --> 18:50.972
One second, please.
Philip, it's Mr. Firth from the law firm.

18:55.179 --> 18:56.510
Hello, Mr. Firth?

18:57.982 --> 18:58.971
Y es.

18:59.750 --> 19:02.116
