for a second interview.

19:17.435 --> 19:20.199
I'm rich! I'm rich!

19:21.372 --> 19:23.135
I'll pack our bags.

19:23.207 --> 19:26.040
Maybe we can get a place
close to the Reagans.

19:27.778 --> 19:30.338
Did I ever tell you folks
how much I like visiting?

19:32.683 --> 19:34.810
Hold on, now. Hold on.

19:35.019 --> 19:36.077
Now look...

19:36.220 --> 19:39.417
even if I do get this job, nothing changes.

19:40.091 --> 19:43.185
This is our home
and this community is a part of our family.

19:45.029 --> 19:46.894
And I'll never turn my back on it.

19:55.306 --> 19:57.536
We had some good times in this old place.

19:58.576 --> 20:00.009
We sure did, baby.

20:01.779 --> 20:03.269
Our roots are here.

20:04.014 --> 20:05.914
This is where we started our family.

20:06.150 --> 20:08.641
Man, I wonder if that
